"Zhihui Xiaoxiang" 2021 China International Rail Transit and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit Opens - Rolling News - Hunan Daily Network - Huasheng Online
Hunan Daily reported on December 10 (reporter Zhou Zhiheng of the full media) that the "Zhihui Xiaoxiang" 2021 China International Rail Transit and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit opened in Zhuzhou on the 9th.
The provincial standing committee and the head of the provincial organization department, Wang Cheng, attended the opening ceremony and delivered a speech.
Wang Cheng pointed out that holding the talent summit is an important measure to implement the spirit of the central talent work conference and the 12th provincial party congress, demonstrating Hunan's sincere commitment to valuing, longing for, and using talents.
Hunan has a good tradition of recognizing, loving, and respecting talents, a broad platform for supporting talent development, and favorable conditions for realizing a better life. In recent years, Hunan has implemented the talent-led development strategy in depth, taking the Furong Talent Action Plan as a lead, and building a complete talent work pattern from attracting, retaining, and using talents. It has become a fertile land for talent growth and achievement, a hot land for innovation and entrepreneurship, and a happy land for living and working.
Currently, Hunan is comprehensively implementing the "Three Highs and Four New" strategic positioning and mission, further opening the door for talent recruitment, and providing more favorable policies, concentrated resources, and better conditions for talent innovation and entrepreneurship. It is expected that outstanding talents from all walks of life will join forces for Hunan's high-quality development.
The event set up exhibition halls in Changsha, Zhuzhou, Xiangtan, and the Hunan Free Trade Zone, and the Provincial Science and Technology Department, the Provincial Industry and Information Technology Department, and the Provincial Human Resources and Social Security Department released lists of key innovation demands in advanced manufacturing-related industries, intelligent manufacturing talent demands, and postdoctoral intelligent manufacturing talent demands in young people.
48 large companies such as China CNR, China National Heavy Duty Truck Group, and CRRC Times Electric are on site to recruit talent, and nearly a thousand recent graduates and social talents in relevant fields participated in the talent project docking.